  <brief_title>Brain Oxygenation and Function of Preterm Newborns During Administration of Two Different Surfactant Preparations</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of the Cerebral Tissue Oxygenation and the Bioelectrical Brain Activity of Preterm Newborns During Administration of Two Different Surfactant</official_title>
  <sponsors>
